https://code.kx.com/dashboards/canvascharts/

# Canvas Chart - KX Dashboards

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/dashboards/canvascharts/

# Canvas Chart

A custom chart builder using HTML Canvas.

## Set up

  1. Add a layer, select the chart type from the dropdown.

  2. Assign the _data source_ to use.

  3. Define the _X-Axis ID_ and _Y-Axis ID_ to plot from your _data source_

  4. Add x axis and y axis labels, and set the _Format_ for each axis.

  5. Un-check _OffsetGridLines_ to position a line at the zero value of the y-axis. 

  6. Use highlight rules to create a color differential in your displayed values; e.g. between positive and negative values. 

  7. Map view states to _Min_ and _Max Viewstate_ to track the viewable range of the chart. 

## Basics

![Screenshot](../img/canvas/canvasbasics.png)

_Name_

    A name for the component provided by the user. 
_Selected_

    A [View State Parameter](../viewstateparameters/) to store the X-axis value at the selected position; e.g time or date 
_Focus_

     [Linking](../viewstateparameters/#linking-components)
_Hover_

    A [View State Parameter](../viewstateparameters/) which stores the X-axis value contingent on where the hover bar is on the chart; e.g. time or date
_Transpose_

    

Check to switch data from Y- to X-axis and X- to Y-axis.

Horizontal Bar Chart

To create a Horizontal Bar Chart, create a standard Bar Chart but check the
_Transpose_ box.

![Screenshot](../img/canvas/horizontalchartbar.jpg)

Note, there is no Zoom support for Horizontal Bar Chart.

_Sort By_

    Defines the sort order for the x-axis, by either the data source index or the x-axis values

## Layers

![Screenshot](../img/canvas/layerselect.jpg)

Create a Line, Bar, Bubble, Violin, Box Plot, Waterfall or Candlestick chart

### Basics

![Screenshot](../img/canvas/canvasbasics2.jpg)

_Data Source_

     [Data sources](../datasources/)
_Name_

    Name used as the chart legend label
_Enabled_

    Toggles display of the data layer on the chart. Can be tied to a [View State Parameter](../viewstateparameters/).
_Legend Enabled_

    Toggles display of data legend. 
_Background Color_

_Background Opacity_

_Border Color_

_Border Opacity_

_Border Width_

    Color, opacity and width for Line, Bar or Bubble charts; opacity has a value between 0 (transparent) and 100 (full opacity). _Border Width_ is in pixels. 
    

Line charts do not require _Background Color_ or _Background Opacity_.

Change layer order

Use a click-and-drag to rearrange the orders of the layer on the chart. The
last layer will be the top layer.

![Screenshot](../img/canvas/dragdroplayer.jpg)

