Check control to parse bars in a Y-axis stack
![Screenshot](../img/canvas/stackedyaxis.jpg)

Stacked Y-axis with Line Fill

Stacking stacks lines in numeric order. Line 1 will be the first (highest)
line down to the last and lowest line, closest to origin X-axis. Line fill
will change accordingly. For example, a line fill with or without Y-axes
stacking enabled:

[![Screenshot](../img/canvas/yaxesstackline.jpg)](../img/canvas/yaxesstackline.jpg
"Click to expand")

_Position_

    Position Y-axis label to the `left` or `right` of chart area.
_Center_

    Set center value for `linear` Y-axis. 

